headline: CSX Corporation Announces Date for Fourth Quarter Earnings Release and Earnings Call
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Dec. 18, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) will release fourth quarter financial and operating results after the market close on Thursday, January 23, 2025.
